wikipedia_page.main: Willie McCallum is Scottish Highland bagpipe player.

response: *2021 Jack Lee, Canada - 3rd Win, Willie McCallum sets new record of 10th MSR win
*2016 Roddy MacLeod, Glasgow - 5th Win, record-breaking 10th Piobaireachd win, Willie McCallum sets record 8th MSR Win
*2005 Willie McCallum, Glasgow - 8th Win (Willie McCallum wins both individual events)
*2004 Willie McCallum, Glasgow - 7th Win (Willie McCallum wins both individual events)

McCallum Bagpipes is a company that manufactures Great Highland bagpipes. Founded in 1998, it is based in Kilmarnock, Scotland. The company has worked with bagpiper Willie McCallum to design several products.
